headline: Skyworks Introduces Expanded Wi-Fi 7 Portfolio with Next-Generation, High-Efficiency and High-Performance Front-End Modules and Filters
summary: PARIS, October 14, 2025--Skyworks Solutions, Inc. (Nasdaq: SWKS), a global leader in high-performance analog and mixed-signal semiconductors, today introduced the expansion of its Wi-Fi 7 portfolio. Skyworks’ new comprehensive lineup of front-end modules (FEMs) and bulk acoustic wave (BAW) filters are designed to enhance range and coverage across 2.4 GHz, 5 GHz, and 6 GHz bands.
